ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家係生係死都唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5488e21eb12ee312a1967cdedad01d0da43fbe74","tid":229534,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69b364e99e9dbb745e540a1b82146633cdd52f4e","tid":229534,"uid":42527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d74df2c3ede8dd22d06be159ee7af33a4f6257a","tid":229534,"uid":101282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男朋友迫我扮豬"},{"pid":"17ab4956ec2ef641cb36e605fda739f27298a307","tid":229534,"uid":58623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:33:04.000Z","msg":"ex話後來呢首歌代表佢想同我講嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22ec9065c14b5459f0b0943eac5ad8ba6ccb900","tid":229534,"uid":29745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"成日俾人咁叫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c012ac6d1b6fe0bf59b6ebff4eec68881be68cf6","tid":229534,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:37:23.000Z","msg":"擅長爬樹既朋友"},{"pid":"4bc25d1010256bf30f690b6dfbbeb8418e4fb39e","tid":229534,"uid":12438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"進化階段:究極體<br />\n　　屬性：疫苗<br />\n　　種族：古代龍型官方說明<br />\n　　存在感和能力都很大地超過其他的數碼獸。可是，因為那個強大的力量很難控制，被分成了善與惡兩種。也有釋放了全部力量的形態（戰士形態/Fighter Mode 及被視為最終形態的聖騎士形態），不過，見過的人非常地少。 <br />\n<br />\n　　根據第二部玄內的講述，帝皇龍甲獸環遊全世界一周只需不足三十分鐘，飛行速度很快。<br />\n　　順帶一提的是，帝皇龍甲獸亦可以在外太空飛行（詳情請見第二部第４０集），是少數可以離開地球飛行的數碼寶貝之一。<br />\n<br />\n必殺技<br />\n　　光子鐳射（Positron Laser）：從背中發射能源炮的技能（可一次性發射多束）。 <br />\n　　超級死亡（Mega Death）：通過發射超重量級別的黑暗物質，用黑暗的力量吞噬以自身為半徑數百米內範圍所有物質的技能。 <br />\n<br />\n　　初次進化歷程：v仔獸和蟲蟲獸在數碼世界受到木乃伊獸和亞基利獸襲擊，進化成機甲龍獸。數碼暴龍再次出現在現實世界，而且在日本各地都有！大輔聽到阿賢住的地方有數碼暴龍出現，便決定單獨去接小賢。三角龍獸出現在那裡，大輔趕到后破壞黑暗塔並讓機甲龍獸去與三角龍獸戰鬥。這時，變年輕的玄內出現在眾孩子面前，並拿出青龍獸身上的一顆數碼珠，放出神聖力量，大家都可以進化成完全體，機甲龍獸還進化成帝皇龍甲獸。"},{"pid":"d490ce9f4c00541d327641fe36164d8d54030b37","tid":229534,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:45:05.000Z","msg":"肥婆落下心中不必驚慌"},{"pid":"608f2b638c320a97a991037efb2cd38414be570e","tid":229534,"uid":90759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"呀朗又戴帽"},{"pid":"ccf9efa054999f00e4fd57b14bc46407a1d58e11","tid":229534,"uid":114518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"User name係其中一個人生目標<br />\n加上新account諗唔到改乜名好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0870337f0ca85567ddff95a1bb663fce04236c8d","tid":229534,"uid":109761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf33e898f38adaa8ed8580657f0026313b31318","tid":229534,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"英文名嘅中文解釋 再斷章取義下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6fd23ad283821884bf664e299026136d1d1ad4","tid":229534,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"我一回 啲post會沉底<br />\n希望打破宿命"},{"pid":"edd1fd85a783844f185cc9b496d253a70f743ee4","tid":229534,"uid":80418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"好想做Hana老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown